snippet.title: Regalia: Royal Edition - Reveal Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Regalia is a tactical RPG about the restoration of a fallen kingdom to its former glory. Embark on an adventure that will remind you of your best jRPG experiences. Coming to PS4 in Q1 2018.
